df_reservations_country = df[df['is_canceled'] == 0]['country'].value_counts().reset_index()
df_reservations_country.columns = ['country', 'reservations']

df_reservations_country.loc[df_reservations_country['reservations']<100, 'country']='OTHERS'
df_reservations_country=df_reservations_country.groupby('country').sum('reservations')
df_reservations_country=df_reservations_country.rename_axis('country').reset_index()
